column5: Last day of walleye in NWO.Got invited to use a boat over at Clarks Camp on Edward Lake as they have one dock in and a Kodiak.Quite a bit of snow up there.Bit on the cool side but we'll worth the 2 hrs i spent fishing.Caught a couple dozen fish.Normally would still be ice fishing.
Nice eaters john,looks like fun to me snow or no snow,least someone is wetting a line
Thank you for posting, John. I guess the only way we can get our NWO "fix" is through your posts and pictures.
I'll keep trying.There trying to keep us from leaving our houses now.
Sneak out the back door they won't see you and wear camo and also a Halloween mask,they won't recognize you,good luck and may the force be with you
I would most likely be the only person on the lake. The police seem they don't want to get involved in the Gestapo act the government is imposing on us.
Well if the gestapo chase you on the lake run them up on a rock reef john,just like in the movies,nickname you,john bond 00-1800

They won't be on the lake.Theyll wait by my truck.At least I would get some undisturbed fish√¨ng in for the day.-8 here this morning.As week goes on it will be getting warmer.No rush to get out.Thurs 14c and sunny looks like the day to go.
